  • Constructor Details

    • Vaccine

      public Vaccine(String line)
      Constructs a Vaccine object by parsing a line from the CSV file. The data on the line is in the order: country, date, vaccinations. Where there the number of vaccinations are missing, it is set to 0.
      Parameters:
      line - a line of the CSV file

    • Vaccine

      public Vaccine(String country, String date)
      Constructs a Vaccine object with the given country and date. The vaccinations are set to 0.
      Parameters:
      country - the country which the vaccinations are from
      date - the date these vaccinations took place
